import React from 'react'
import Simple from './Components/Simple'
import appan from './Components/'
import lord from './lord.jpg'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Simple name="Muruga"place="Thiruchendhur"img={appan}/>
    <Simple name="Kathirvela" place="Palani"img={lord}/>
    <Simple name="Senthil" place="Thovalai"/>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
